properties.Name: BondStatus
properties.Description:
The current status of the bond.

Ex:  

In Default
A bond that ceases to pay interest (because the issuer has financial problems) is in default of the terms of the bond agreement, and is said to be in default.

Performing
In compliance with bond terms and conditions.
